{"tid":1555013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日仲同狗既家人做朋友係乜心態","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T11:14:33.000Z","uid":124322,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74477f373218adfb73714403b93b5ffdb2831185","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n囗講幾憎黑警 要憎一世 要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後又可以同黑警啲家人做朋友 一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工已經做唔到 又唔洗你上前線檔子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n杯葛警察家屬咁簡單都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再講咩憎黑警啦 講出黎尷唔尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去撐警集會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好好笑 原來自己身邊既人連咁簡單既事都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲家屬有份用佢打市民啲ot錢去旅行食好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到HA Secret 未 去得現場既前線都係自願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑死 繼續口講憎黑警身體繼續做朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a93bb6d231534f178180e671dc986b5dcaf05d","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"搵番啲舊post<br />\n十幾日前先有巴打po咗篇文話要同所有同警有關係既人保持距離<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在塞爾維亞的民主運動之中，他們曾經遇到一個特別殘暴的警察局長。在他管轄的小城裡面，他彷彿國王一樣濫用權力、肆無忌憚。崔甘娜嫌惡地抿著嘴巴：『他特別享受毒打、刑求他人的樂趣。人越不成形他越樂。』所以歐特普認為可能沒辦法說服他，至少無法直接跟他講理。<br />\n<br />\n於是他們拍下他毒打『歐特普』年輕成員的照片，製作成海報，上面公開他的姓名與行動電話。然後他們把這些海報貼在他太太會去購物的商場，還貼在他小孩去幼稚園上學的路上。海報上要求市民打電話給他，問他為什麼毒打我們的小孩。他的太太非常震驚，全家人也很快就成為全城的拒絕往來戶。崔甘娜說：『我們不攻擊穿制服的他。我們透過他太太，攻擊在家裡的他。我們才不讓那個惡棍可以躲在制度或者警徽之後。』<br />\n<br />\n這個例子引起了很大的迴響。一位運動人士表示：『就是有這些令人髮指的人物，他們躲在政權的庇蔭下。他們就是暴政的具體象徵。』在場的人都點頭表示同意。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 威廉．道布森：《獨裁者的進化：收編、分化、假民主》(台北：左岸文化)第七章，第356頁。"},{"pid":"cac74588d23ec16c5827e9c478ed3c840c4151ee","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"咁簡單都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb288aa7c52f9cdcca677207420a33a59f06e76","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"要求呢啲人唔好再講憎黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af513f8bc98a1f786961629abc369493b5ade01e","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"同殺人犯做朋友有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb436712a3e3c07a0dc877f1445051636abbf896","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"同強姦犯做朋友有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18523f78092fdcab4c4635b0961926e0009decf6","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"同性罪犯做朋友有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa2fa33420138790a888604c59243055b2e27fb","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"同虐待狂做朋友有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf5c90542f428864f205753a45d7afa8e052dfd","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"有冇尊重過義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0bea86d3936fdf49412a795178de3cc15558cb","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"冇任何代價既杯葛都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8815378740e9e979f1b12906908ee36e241cd0","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"仲話光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d72cd9729440dce1101c268843ec65d4d7bc989","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"冇成本既杯葛都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35fd4cc683f3efd41cd9f833749109df6857f4f","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:05:56.000Z","msg":"繼續同用強姦犯啲錢既人做朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62065081efba1d2bc328bcff5323d4ffb770be8f","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"續同用殺人犯啲錢既人做朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec5910c6205d7efa149feb42d1847a485690ce1","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"續同用性罪犯啲錢既人做朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a246daf22e34d4cee5848bd74f45bfaa7550793e","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"睇黎好多人仲同緊黑警家人做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196928e2f3a28e0c162f0f194aee2e5c33a24e41","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"有白警就一就流出情報啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6de88d4072e47868df8ba931a2708f512495346","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"諗諗下又係既 同特權階級做朋友又唔係咁易既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af70c3c2be34df61f1dd959a15ce2b3e4e6de6c","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dc37f69783a7be576a3f3ecbf7daa0b94046b3","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"連最簡單既都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614448065ad20c75837298ee4dc26db2d4435731","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"你會唔會同林奠個仔做朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71575899dddc40ba25955e242d1adc073d0dced4","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會同鄧賊做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896a77b78de35f5492f58ecac580fc5ae95b60cf","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"自推咗咁多次都冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffedfdad7d40ef7d0af158c98aeebc250e23cfb4","tid":1555013,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2f5aca79fa7ebe18c645671cab19b6981a401f","tid":1555013,"uid":81336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"唔識D咁既人wo"}]}